channel.description:
Welcome to TehDevScape v3! and yes i know i had to stop 508's but they was funnier to code so i think i Keep Making 508's And Releasing Them Here!
Guys Much Thanks for 112 rep ++ Next i Hope i get 200! Thank you all! [size=12pt]Guys Pm me what should i make to v4?[/size]
[IMG]http://i1270.photobucket.com/albums/jj601/im1prins1/logo-2.png[/img]
[size=24pt]I do NOT give permission to re-release/release This anywhere without my PERMISSION! :)[/size]
Okay I Start about Thing's i've Done to v3. ------------------------------------------ -Good old Home :) -Finished ::godtrain area! -Added INADE! ::inade! w00t :) -Added Barrows! ::barrows -Fixed few error's for no disconnecting. -Made Staffzone For mods+ ::staffzone -Added Jad! -Added Bandos boss/ command is ::boss -Added saradomin boss/ Command is ::boss -added new starter! -added zammy boss/ Command is ::boss -Fixed Fight Pits! :):) -Many New Commands! As : ::starter i added there some necks for you can tele diffrent place's as fightpits,cw,agility. And much much more!
For The Bosse's and Barrow's you have to make Teleport's ill create the code for you : just put this code to commands.java Barrows : if(cmd[0].startsWith("barrows") && p.cmb == 1){ p.frames.sendMessage(p, "<img=1><img=1>Welcome to New Barrows!<img=1><img=1>"); p.teleportTo(2899 + Misc.random(2), 3559 + Misc.random(2), 0, 4, 0, 8939, 3164, 3485, 0, 1577, 0);
Bosse's : if(cmd[0].startsWith("boss") && p.cmb == 1){ p.frames.sendMessage(p, "<img=1>Gl With Bosse's!.<img=1>"); p.teleportTo(2446 + Misc.random(2), 3090 + Misc.random(2), 0, 4, 0, 8939, 8941, 1576, 0, 1577, 0); ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[IMG]http://i1270.photobucket.com/albums/jj601/im1prins1/pictures.png[/img] Pics : [IMG]http://i1270.photobucket.com/albums/jj601/im1prins1/starter.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1270.photobucket.com/albums/jj601/im1prins1/barrowsarea.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1270.photobucket.com/albums/jj601/im1prins1/floorplaces.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1270.photobucket.com/albums/jj601/im1prins1/afterfloor.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1270.photobucket.com/albums/jj601/im1prins1/fightpits.png[/img] Good old Home! :) (and hd client) [IMG]http://i1270.photobucket.com/albums/jj601/im1prins1/hdclient.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1270.photobucket.com/albums/jj601/im1prins1/staffzone1.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1270.photobucket.com/albums/jj601/im1prins1/inadeboss.png[/img] [IMG]http://i1270.photobucket.com/albums/jj601/im1prins1/enjoyedsource.png[/img]
Okay For Running Source Code is This : @echo off color 0a title Starting... echo. echo TehDeScape is Running.. Server Status = ONLINE echo. cd ../bin title W00t v3! "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.7.0_05\bin\java.exe" palidino76/rs2/Server 43594 pause
For Running Client Code is This :
@echo off java -classpath out/production/508" "HD;lib/hdlibs.jar;lib/substance.jar client 16 live live software members english game0 pause
